rows.label: qst201618_msg0002

Time to let [ML:TownFlag digit=F16 value=1 ] fans of friend Nanakoori
hear beautiful music!

Y-y-yes! Yes, yes.
I'm fi-fi-fi-fine! Yes.

rows.label: qst201618_msg0008

rows.label: qst201618_msg0009

rows.label: qst201618_msg0011

Okay, I know, I know.
I've practiced a lot, so everything
will be fine if I just do it like that...

rows.label: qst201618_msg0013
rows.name:
Breathe in... Breathe out...
Phew, okay.

rows.label: qst201618_msg0014
rows.name:
Thanks, that did calm me down
somewhat.

rows.label: qst201618_msg0015
rows.name:
I'll give it all I've got!
That...may not be much, though...
